kind of awesome, you know.

12:13.733 --> 12:14.818
To be honest, I...

12:14.984 --> 12:17.195
- Really kind of miss it.
- I said hog ring.

12:17.361 --> 12:19.156
"Hog ring".
Yeah.

12:19.322 --> 12:21.111
I-I love Ava.

12:21.236 --> 12:22.712
It's just that...

