halfway, you know?

12:30.210 --> 12:32.252
Thanks, man.
You know, I just...

12:32.418 --> 12:35.338
Feel like I...
I don't know, I'd rather have

12:35.504 --> 12:36.623
what you and Reagan have, you know?

12:36.748 --> 12:38.858
Something solid and comfortable.

12:38.983 --> 12:42.928
Yeah, although I gotta say,
I wish sometimes that I would

12:43.053 --> 12:45.223
do something crazy
like throw a shoe or...

