14:12.658 --> 14:14.235
Another thing that you
might want to hold on

14:14.360 --> 14:18.004
to your ear hoops
over there, but, uh...

14:18.129 --> 14:19.609
I have a baby.
I do.

14:19.997 --> 14:22.998
Yeah, you heard me.
I do.

14:26.202 --> 14:28.446
You ever have one of
those moments when you, like,

14:28.571 --> 14:31.682
