Yeah, you know what?

14:39.213 --> 14:43.459
I'm not gonna do this tattoo today.

14:43.584 --> 14:45.260
Maybe tomorrow?
I just, uh...

14:45.426 --> 14:47.430
I forget I, um,
am late for a pap smear,

14:47.555 --> 14:49.131
so thank you very much.

14:49.256 --> 14:51.182
Take care.
Keep the deposit.

15:06.947 --> 15:10.250
Yeah, this is totally gonna work.

