with Italian ingredients.

16:04.755 --> 16:06.675
- Oh.
- Mmm.

16:06.800 --> 16:08.510
- Ah?
- Mmm... uhh.

16:08.676 --> 16:11.513
To be the food
going down your food tube.

16:11.679 --> 16:12.445
What?

16:12.570 --> 16:13.579
You have such an instinct

16:13.704 --> 16:14.766
for the finer things in life.

16:14.932 --> 16:16.781
The way you dress, the car you drive,

16:16.906 --> 16:18.395
even your classic French timepiece.

16:18.561 --> 16:20.484
- It's a Piaget.
- Ah, yes.

16:20.609 --> 16:24.721
Julian, I'm sorry, we've been
talking about me for an hour.

16:24.846 --> 16:26.403
I'm bored. Can we
talk about something else?

16:26.569 --> 16:28.655
Understood.
I'm not a man to be told twice.

16:28.821 --> 16:30.198
Thank you.

16:30.364 --> 16:32.367
You have the most beautiful
freckle right there.

16:32.533 --> 16:34.195
- [Sighs]
- And here.

16:34.320 --> 16:36.371
- And here, and here.
- Okay.

16:36.537 --> 16:37.829
You're a freckle face.

16:37.954 --> 16:39.457
Okay, Julian.
You know what?

16:39.623 --> 16:41.563
You've actually cleared
something up for me.

16:41.688 --> 16:43.044
- Okay.
- I gotta go.

16:43.210 --> 16:44.170
- Gotta go?
- Yeah.

16:44.336 --> 16:45.299
- But...
- I just...

16:45.424 --> 16:46.423
Why you gonna go?

16:46.589 --> 16:48.466
- I can't get...
- Okay, wait, I do this.

16:48.632 --> 16:49.801
- Hold on.
- I'm dynamite!

16:49.967 --> 16:51.672
- [Plates clattering]
- All right, there we go.

16:51.797 --> 16:53.373
- Yep.
- Thank you.

16:53.498 --> 16:56.224
I'll just see my way out.

16:56.390 --> 16:58.675
Honey, you okay?

16:58.800 --> 17:00.603
- Yeah.
- What's go...

17:00.769 --> 17:01.813
[Gasps]

