17:23.375 --> 17:24.932
Aww.

17:25.057 --> 17:26.337
- Yeah.
- Next to the dolphin?

17:26.502 --> 17:28.367
I was gonna have
the dolphin jumping over him

17:28.492 --> 17:30.300
and then splashing all happy.

17:30.466 --> 17:33.439
Oh, well, it doesn't matter.

17:33.564 --> 17:35.263
I guess that kind of stuff's
a thing of the past, huh?

17:35.429 --> 17:37.348
Yeah.
[Peal of thunder]

17:37.514 --> 17:39.344
You know what?
We should probably pick up

17:39.469 --> 17:41.813
- some cash for the sitter.
- Uh, I think they have...

17:41.938 --> 17:43.396
Yeah, they have
an ATM right over there.

17:43.562 --> 17:45.565
Aw, that's one of those ones
that charges, like, three bucks.

17:45.731 --> 17:48.352
