17:53.516 --> 17:54.825
and my hair looks really good today,

17:54.950 --> 17:56.994
so no, I'm not hopping out.
You hop out.

17:57.119 --> 17:58.529
Well, I just slid down a wall for...

17:58.654 --> 17:59.996
Fine, yeah, okay.
I'll hop out.

